#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:1
msgid "Hercules DJControl Compact"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:4
msgid ""
"[Manufacturer’s product "
"page](https://support.hercules.com/en/product/djcontrolcompact-en/)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:6
msgid ""
"The Hercules DJControl Compact is a simple controller for basic two-channel "
"mixing. This device does not have a built in sound card, so it would require"
" a {ref}`splitter cable <hardware-splitter-cables>` or {ref}`separate audio "
"interface <hardware-audio-interfaces>` to be able to preview tracks in "
"headphones. It also does not have buttons for routing decks to headphones."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:13
msgid ""
"Thanks to Hercules for supporting the development of this mapping by "
"providing a controller."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:18
msgid "Mapping description"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:21
msgid ""
"Much of the Compact’s behavior is hard-coded into its firmware, including "
"shift button messages and button mode selections."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:24
msgid "Shift + Play jumps to the beginning of the track and stops playback."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:26
msgid ""
"The cue button behaves differently depending on the {ref}`cue mode set in "
"Mixxx’s Preferences <interface-cue-modes>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:28
msgid ""
"The sync button synchronizes the tempo to the other deck. Press and hold "
"sync to engage {ref}`Sync Lock <sync-lock>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:31
msgid ""
"There is only one each of the Mode, Shift, and Scratch buttons, so they "
"affect both decks."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:34
msgid "Shift + Scratch (Automix) toggles AutoDJ on/off."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:36
msgid "Jog Wheels"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:39
msgid ""
"When Scratch is off, turning a jog wheel bends the pitch of the track. When "
"Scratch is on, turning a jog wheel scratches that deck. Holding Shift and "
"turning a jog wheel adjusts the playback rate (tempo). Enable keylock on a "
"deck by clicking the music note button on screen if you do not want the "
"pitch to change when adjusting the tempo."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:45
msgid "Pad Grid"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:48
msgid "Press the MODE button to cycle through each pad mode."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:50
msgid "Loop mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:53
msgid ""
"In loop mode, the buttons are mapped in a way that’s more artistically "
"expressive:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:56
msgid "Button 1 enables and disables the loop"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:57
msgid "Button 2 enables an 8 beat loop"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:58
msgid "Button 3 divides the current loop in half"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:59
msgid "Button 4 doubles the length of the current loop"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:60
msgid "Shift + Button 1 performs an 1/8th beat roll"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:61
msgid "Shift + Button 2 performs an 1/4th beat roll"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:62
msgid "Shift + Button 3 performs an 1/2th beat roll"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:63
msgid "Shift + Button 4 performs an 1 beat roll"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:65
msgid "FX mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:68
msgid "Button 1 enables and disables the first FX chain for Channel 1"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:69
msgid "Button 2 enables and disables the second FX chain for Channel 1"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:70
msgid "Button 1 enables and disables the first FX chain for Channel 2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:71
msgid "Button 2 enables and disables the second FX chain for Channel 2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:73
msgid "Shift-FX buttons are not mapped."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:75
msgid "Sampler mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:78
msgid "Left side buttons play Sample Decks 1 through 4"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:79
msgid "Right side buttons play Sample Decks 5 through 8"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:80
msgid ""
"Shift + Buttons stops Sample Deck and puts the playhead at the cue point"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:83
msgid "Cue mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:86
msgid "Each button activates the hotcue with that number"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_compact.md:87
msgid "Shift + button clears the hotcue with that number"
msgstr ""
